snippet.title: Dance Eden | A multiplayer XR dance game
snippet.description:
🎮 Dance Eden – A multiplayer XR dance game developed by DigiEden is now live with a free demo! In the game, you can dance solo or join other players to experience immersive dancing together.
🚀 Free Demo Now Live on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2934620/DANCE_EDEN/
💃 Whether you're a dance enthusiast or just looking for a new gaming experience, Dance Eden has something for everyone! Come join us and feel the rhythm!
🥳 Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/ZTMAF2WPJP
